c: 17
v: 101
t: "Nummah Yalli Nabii Muusah sagla astay baxxaqqa itta kaah necee iyye, tokkel Nabii Mucammadow {zsak atu israa-iil xayloh tutaaxago Nabii Muusa Yalli kaah yeceeh yan astooti luk keenik tatre maraa kee firqawnâ fanah yemeeteeh firqawni diggah anu Muusaw elle baaben numuy kas edde yengeyyeh koo dareema kaak iyye waqdi ken esserey}"